Description:
AMAZING OPPORTUNITY IN DOCKLANDS
Whether you are a first home buyer or an astute investor, don’t miss out on this incredible chance to buy in the Docklands.
Located on La Trobe Street where Docklands meets the CBD sits the Lacrosse Building, ideally located next to Marvel Stadium, public transport, restaurants and shopping.
With current high returns, this 2 bed, 2 bath apartment has fantastic views of the CBD, includes a modern kitchen with stone bench tops and dishwasher, mirrored built in robes in the bedrooms, and clean, contemporary finishes in the bathrooms. A Euro-laundry and private balcony round out this well designed apartment.
This apartment is completed by split system heating & cooling, secure swipe and intercom entry, as well as use of the outdoor pool and gym. Whether you’re enjoying eating out with friends, swimming, shopping, or attending sporting events at Marvel Stadium, this is low maintenance living without the price tag.

Description:
A Yarra Point Inspiration with amazing size and modern class
Lofty and luxurious in the Yarra Point complex, this 26th floor apartments proportioned living spaces merge seamlessly with mesmerising outlooks. The light-filled and relaxed living and dining provides a sizeable area suited for morning breakfasts and lazing in front of the TV after a long day at work. This zone further opens out to a balcony where you can enjoy summer sunsets with wine or beer in hand.
The stone kitchen has a high end feel with luxe benchtops, island bench, and stainless steel Miele appliances. Spectacularly modern in style the stunning interior also boasts a study nook, five-star master ensuite bedroom with its own private balcony, two more bedrooms with built-in robes, a second bathroom and a separate laundry, ducted heating and cooling, secure intercom and two secure car spaces. Onsite facilities include a gymnasium, roof top herb garden, business center, library, secured bike storage room and secure visitor car park and well as access to RekDek gym, pool, spa, steam room, and sauna.
Surrounded by green parklands, youll love this stunning Yarras Edge precinct close to South Wharf Promenade with restaurants and bars, local eateries including The General Assembly, Charlie Lovett, Munich Brauhaus and The Boatbuilders Yard. Youre also a short walk to the DFO shopping, CBD and Southbank attractions, Crown Casino, trams, and Southern Cross Station.

Description:
Style and Sophistication with Brilliant Blue-Water Views
This sun-drenched and style-driven 2 bedroom, 2 bathroom apartment in the tightly held Nolan Tower dazzles and delights with blissful, blue-water views over Victoria Harbour and Port Phillip Bay. Head downstairs and live the life you love within walking distance of Newquay Promenade restaurants, Docklands Stadium, the CBD, Costco, Harbour Town Shopping Centre, free city trams, and Southern Cross Station.
Brilliantly bright with sleek tiling underfoot, discover a deluxe kitchen, topped with black granite and showcasing stainless-steel appliances. Effortlessly alluring, roomy open-plan living and dining is framed by impressive panels of floor-to-ceiling, double-glazed glass boasting an uninterrupted waterside panorama that will energise you every day. Step outside and relax on your very own private balcony, sharing the same spectacular views and capturing summer sea breezes with ease. Both large bedrooms are equipped with panel heating, extensive built-in robes and the main bedroom comes complete with its own fully tiled ensuite. The family-sized bathroom offers a luxurious bath, separate walk-in shower and a marble-finished vanity.
Prominently positioned on the 18th floor, special features include a concealed laundry, secure parking, blockout roller blinds, ducted heating/cooling, video intercom entry, ample storage, and exclusive access to resort-style facilities including a swimming pool and a fully equipped gym. Experience luxury living at every turn and make this exceptional apartment your home, city base or blue-chip investment today!
* Photo identification will be required upon entering the property at the inspection time.

Description:
Best value for the best building of Docklands
Located in the luxurious 'Convesso', this 5 star building has set the benchmark for all future living within the Docklands precinct. This stylish apartment comprises of two spacious bedrooms, a designer kitchen, stone bench tops, refrigerator and an abundance of cupboard space, a wide balcony perfect for entertaining or relaxing, two boutique hotel style bathrooms, ducted air conditioning and heating, one secure undercover car space and a storage cage.
With a level of amenity similar to that of exclusive 5-star boutique hotels, the Convesso offers:
- 24-hour concierge
- Residents Lounge
- Business Centre & Board Room
- Cinema (within the Concavo building)
- North facing Sky Garden facing the water, with BBQ facilities
- 25-meter pool, spa, and sauna
- Gymnasium and treatment room
Don't miss a fantastic opportunity to secure this apartment right by the waterside!

Description:
Wake up to stunning Victoria Harbour views
This 2 bedroom, 2 bathroom residence will be the perfect match for buyers who wants an apartment that promises fantastic quality, space and beautiful Victoria Harbour views.
Situated in the Palladio complex in the excellent New Quay precinct
Relaxed and open central living and dining zone
Well-sized covered balcony features a south-west orientation allowing for superb harbour views
Deluxe kitchen just off the entry offers a sizeable breakfast bar and stainless steel European appliances
Master bedroom includes an ensuite, 2nd bedroom with private balcony
Built-in robes in both bedrooms
Well-appointed bathroom, concealed separate laundry
Reverse cycle heating and cooling, wall heating in bedrooms
Secure intercom entry
Secure undercover car space
AMENITIES
Designed by renowned Fender Katsalidis, The Palladio complex allows residents access to an exclusive health club featuring rooftop pool, private function area, and fully-equipped gym with stunning views.
LOCATION
The fantastic NewQuay precinct is just moments to Marvel Stadium, Capital City Trail, harbourside restaurants, nearby trams including the free City Circle line, Southern Cross Station, and the airport Skybus. Youre also near The District Docklands which features a Hoyts Cinemas, 8 Street hawker food outlets, and a new fresh food precinct opening soon called The Market which will feature butchers, delis, bakeries, coffee roasters, Woolworths supermarket, and Dan Murphys. The CBD is also so close where you have the best in Melbourne at your fingertips.
Please contact Thomas Tregonning on 0437 092 078 to arrange an exclusive inspection

Description:
Stunning CBD View and Standout Location in Docklands
With a spot on the 21st floor of the Lacrosse complex that sits right next to the iconic Marvel Stadium which will have footy and sports fans in a frenzy, this fantastic 2 bedroom, 2 bathroom apartment with stunning city views is a modern gem.
Terrific north-east balcony allows for sensational views of the CBD
Outstanding light fills the sizeable lounge and dining zone
Seamless flow from living to balcony thanks to full sliding doors
Sleek kitchen with stone countertop and stainless steel appliances
Both bedrooms with built-in robe storage
Master bedroom promises a private and stylish ensuite
Luxury central bathroom with rain shower and laundry facilities
Split system heating and cooling
Secure intercom entry
Secure basement car space
AMENITIES
The Lacrosse residential building is a safe and secure complex, which offers residents access to a swimming pool and gymnasium. You also have ILZA Japanese Café located on the ground floor of the building.
LOCATION
The Stadium precinct has you so close to the best of the Docklands as well as being near amazing city attractions. Youre moments to great restaurants and cafes including Tenten Café, MOMANI, Woolshed, and Mama Rumaan, while youre short tram ride up La Trobe Street to Flagstaff Gardens, Queen Victoria Market, Melbourne Central, State Library of Victoria, RMIT University, and QV Melbourne. Southern Cross Station is only a short walk away.
Please contact Mark Sutherland on 0418 691 585 to arrange an exclusive inspection.

Description:
Experience Style and Elegance in Luxurious Gold Tower
Enjoying a stylish contemporary resume in the Gold Tower of the new Aqui development. Currently leased out at $550 per week, this two bedroom apartment blends modern charm with stress-free Docklands living suitable for investors or owner occupiers.
Open plan lounge and dining with quality carpet creates an environment that is relaxed, with this sizeable main hub having direct access to the undercover balcony perfect for weekend meals and drinks. Designer black tapware and quality stone are defining qualities of the kitchen which also has stainless steel Asko appliances.
Both bedrooms offer excellent space and a location right near the attractive bathroom which promises floor-to-ceiling wall tiles and a rain shower, while this apartment also boasts a European laundry, reverse cycle cooling, secure intercom, secure car space, storage cage and access to a 25m indoor pool, spa, sauna, gym, library, private meeting rooms, lush rooftop garden, and secure on-site bicycle storage as part of the building.
Walk to Harbour Town Shopping Centre which has great retail shops as well as eateries including Le Cirque, Nandos, Coffee Club, and Sun Churro. You also have access to waterside restaurants, grocery stores, Moonee Ponds Creek Trail, and the 30, 75, and 86 trams.

Description:
Flawless Victoria Harbour living with superior quality and style
Owning a wonderful corner location, stunning natural light thanks to the bright full windows, and an abundance of magnificent space and stellar contemporary class, this two bedroom apartment in the Dock 5 building is for those who appreciate the finer things in life.
The immense central living and meals zone will be your favourite room of the apartment, with the brilliant open layout, amazing light, and south and east views defining this memorable space. From here you get access to the sizable undercover balcony, where you have wonderful views towards the CBD and Marvel Stadium.
The kitchen will have home cooks giddy with delight thanks to the luxe stone benchtops and stainless steel Miele appliances. Both south-facing bedrooms come with built-in robes, meanwhile the deluxe central bathroom with a separate bath and shower is truly a model of style. You also get an additional powder room, laundry, ducted heating and cooling, intercom entry, secure car space, and access to a swimming pool, gym, and BBQ area.
The Victoria Harbour precinct is a great collection of retail and office spaces giving it that perfect balance of work life and everyday living. Youre close to Buluk Park, Docklands Parks, Library @ The Dock, The Hub @ Docklands, Bourke Street cafes and restaurants, and trams.

Description:
An elite Yarras Edge retreat with water views that will inspire
Relax in style in this 27th floor retreat, which has an enormous central lounge and dining zone which promises beautiful timber flooring underfoot. The wonderful designer kitchen adjoins the central living area and comes with impressive stone benches and splashback, feature island bench, and stainless steel appliances. The main zone further opens out to the balcony which has stunning Yarra River, Bolte Bridge vistas and Port Phillip Bay views.
A master bedroom includes access to its own private balcony area as well as ample built-in robes and a dazzling double vanity ensuite. The 2nd bedroom with BIRs also has entry to the main balcony. In the Yarras Edge precinct, youre close to the brilliant South Wharf Promenade which has a variety of sensational bars and restaurants plus easy access to DFO shopping. Youre also a short trip to Crown Entertainment Complex, Southbank Promenade, and public transport.

Elegance, Class and Truly Spectacular Views
From the clever floorplan and luxurious interiors to remarkable views of the Yarra River and parts of Southbank and the CBD, this elegant two bedroom + study or potential 3rd bedroom, two bathroom apartment is your chance to live the modern Docklands good life.
Bright floor-to-ceiling windows, quality stone benchtops, excellent tapware, and other premium touches is what sets this residence apart from the rest. The large undercover balcony can be accessed via the spacious living and meals zones, with this special alfresco space taking in the beautiful water views with Southbank and city buildings completing the picturesque backdrop.
The opulent kitchen is also practical with an island bench and stainless steel appliances. A dedicated study has its own privacy as do both bedrooms which includes the excellent master bedroom which offers a dual vanity ensuite and another balcony. Also make the most of a gorgeous central bathroom, concealed laundry, ducted heating and cooling, secure intercom and 2 secure car spaces. Onsite facilities include a gymnasium, roof top herb garden, business center, library, secured bike storage room and secure visitor car park and well as access to RekDek gym, pool, spa, steam room, and sauna.
This exceptional location has you positioned just an easy walk to all the delights of South Wharf Promenade which has an array of amazing restaurants including Bangpop, Citizen Café and Bar, and Munich Brauhaus just to name a few. You’re also not far from DFO shopping, Crown Casino, Southbank Promenade, great Southbank, CBD, and South Melbourne attractions, trams, and Southern Cross Station.

The impact is immediate upon entry. Discover a formal entrance hall branching off to a trio of privately staged, sunlit bedrooms, serviced by a super-stylish, family-sized bathroom. The palatial main bedroom comes complete with a wall of mirrored built-in robes, balcony access with a screened door, enticing harbour views, and a fully tiled, twin-vanity ensuite boasting a full size bath.
The home spectacularly opens up to reveal far-reaching, and north-facing, open-plan living and dining, complemented by a glistening, granite-topped kitchen showcasing Smeg appliances and a walk-in pantry. Framed by floor-to-ceiling glass, spill outside to a roomy, wraparound balcony, an idyllic spot to relax, unwind and indulge in the northern sun. Overlooking the waters of Victoria Harbour, the views are incomparable, sweeping across the city skyline and the newly badged Marvel Stadium.
Further appeal is enhanced by a concealed laundry, study nook with built-in desk, ducted heating and cooling throughout, two side-by-side car spaces, storage unit, Holland and block-out blinds, and a temperature-controlled wine cellar, perfect for this summer's entertaining season.
Created by award-winning architect John Wardle, the Dock 5 building is a dazzling delight at first sight, from the tantalising textures in a playful foyer to the prized harbourside address. The premium lifestyle facilities are second-to-none with a 25 metre lap pool, fully fitted gym, a BBQ garden terrace, and a very relaxed library, all at your disposal.
* Photo identification will be required upon entering the property at the inspection time.

Description:
Bright Corner Apartment in the Exclusive NewQuay Precinct
Experience the best in striking modern living that also promises a wonderful corner position, this exceptional and pristine two bedroom apartment has an exclusive position in the Palladio complex.
NewQuay Precinct living has never looked as attractive as this easy care 13th floor retreat. Full floor-to-ceiling windows allows for natural light through the relaxed lounge and meals zone, which offers a handy study nook to make the best of the space on offer.
The stylish kitchen includes stainless steel appliances including a dishwasher, meanwhile the bright and spacious main bedroom comes equipped with built-in robe storage. Other highlights include a 2nd bedroom or potential study, premium bathroom with European laundry, heating and cooling, secure intercom, secure car space and access to a health club with rooftop pool, gym and private function area.
You’ll love the summer months down on the waterfront where you can lap up the breezy lifestyle and enjoy fantastic restaurants which include Cargo, Docklands Pizzeria, Sir Basil and Woolshed. You’re also in close proximity to The District Docklands, IGA supermarket, Marvel Stadium and trams.
To arrange an exclusive viewing, please contact Thomas Tregonning on 0413 317 304.

Description:
Incredible Park and City Views That Will Never be Built Out
This exceptional two bedroom apartment positioned in the Victoria Harbour precinct will impress buyers of all types with its immaculate presentation, considered floorplan, and beautiful views of Docklands Park.
Enjoy the thoughtful open plan layout which promises relaxed space for lounging and dining activities. A charming undercover balcony has sensational views over the park and of Marvel Stadium and Southbank buildings in the distance, and is ideal for alfresco meals and drinks.
The stone kitchen is truly flawless and comes with an island bench and quality stainless steel Miele appliances. Both the bedrooms boast built-in robe storage, with the master bedroom being a fantastic place to retire to at the end of a long day thanks to a pristine ensuite. Also embrace a sleek central bathroom, concealed laundry, split system heating and cooling, video intercom, storage cage, and secure car space.
Access a scenic community garden right next door. You’re also just a 200m stroll to Woolworths and an array of terrific restaurants and cafes on Bourke Street, as well as being close to Marvel Stadium, The Hub @ Docklands, outdoor sporting facilities, Capital City Trail, trams, and Southern Cross Station.
To book an exclusive viewing of this property, please contact Donna Chung 0408 650 128

Description:
Grand Heritage
Don't get stuck in traffic. This fully refurbished apartment is in an ideal location close to all the CBD amenities. It is an east facing, fully furnished loft style apartment in Melbourne's Grandest of buildings. Brimming with charm and character, the unit offers the discerning buyer the comforts of a loft style one bedroom Mezzanine lounge and kitchen dinning. An east facing window provides ample natural light. The building was originally opened in 1893 and refurbished in 1996 to accommodate a mix of serviced and residential apartments. Features include ducted heating and cooling, pool, spa, sauna, and gymnasium, caretaker, piano Bar, restaurant and cafe and a secure ground floor car park. For a private inspection call Richard 0437 250 964

Great Waterfront Location – Easy City Access - Call now for a discussion
Work, play or just relax. Apartment 407 at No. 1 Collins Wharf provides all the options. Great for the investor, owner/occupier or an amazing city getaway. Yarra River outlook from bedroom and living areas opening onto a wide balcony offering an unrivalled waterfront atmosphere.
Superb resident’s facilities include sophisticated entry lobby, private resident’s swimming pool, gym and resident’s entertainment spaces. No.1 Collins Wharf - Melbourne’s new waterfront icon.
